channel.title: Some wierd/lost command on a RSPS
channel.description: I am in search of a ::*command* that I used a long time ago in some servers. It used to teleport me to some cave where I could train my ranged to 99 without even leveling up a single cb level. Anyone remembers this or am I the only one?
